      <data key="d1">"Leaked Credential Detection is a cybersecurity measure aimed at identifying unauthorized access due to leaked credentials."&lt;SEP&gt;"Leaked Credential Detection is a defense measure aimed at identifying compromised passwords and preventing unauthorized access."&lt;SEP&gt;"Leaked Credential Detection is a defense strategy employed by organizations to identify and respond to compromised credentials."</data>
