    </node>
    <node id="&quot;FORCED PASSWORD RESET&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"TECHNOLOGY"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Forced Password Reset is a cybersecurity measure that mandates users to change their passwords, aimed at mitigating potential breaches from credential theft."&lt;SEP&gt;"Forced Password Reset is a security measure implemented by organizations requiring users to change their passwords when a breach is suspected."&lt;SEP&gt;"Forced Password Reset is a security measure that requires users to change their passwords, often after a security breach or potential threat."&lt;SEP&gt;"Forced Password Reset is a security strategy that mandates users to reset their passwords after a security breach or credential leak."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-7e63bd71a2f46a0a14702e26dbb0372d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a7a5bd39de71e6cba00acabb57ae835d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b7deadd8b209fb8a2807207318693df8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-faa3215767525cfd086a2adc2bd61472</data>
